      <T n="text">0xEA1570DA<!--String: "The Kingdom Manager can be accessed from the top of the Manage Worlds screen next to the world name. Here you can view a list of all the Nobles in the Kingdom, the current Tax Level and active Decrees. \n\nSelect <b><font color='#199C2C'>Edit Kingdom Titles</font></b> to <b><font color='#199C2C'>customize the titles</font></b> that are used in the Kingdom. Noble Titles can also be customised from a Noble Sim's Career Panel.\n\nThere are two rows of Noble Titles per career rank. This will display a primary title unlocked by the career, along with a secondary title below, which can be used automatically by your Noble Sim's children."--></T>
    </U>
